column2: Park Plaza Hotels Europe: Save up to 35% On stays until 30 September 2021
column3: Book by 5 September 2021 for stays from 17 May – 30 September 2021 and receive the following: Get up to 35% off our Best Flexible Rate  Fully cancellable (up to 24 hours prior to arrival date)  Fully Flexible rates   Upgrade rooms types available    Non-members 20%   RR members extra 15%. column2: Promotion
column3: Prepaid - 25% Off by booking in advance ! 25% discount on ALL Radisson hotels by booking in advance. Join today to unlock even more exclusive discounts and benefits at all of our hotels worldwide.. - The Prepaid Rate is 5% to 25% off the Best Available Rate at participating hotels, depending on the location of the hotel. - Participating hotels in Europe, the Middle East and Africa offer up to 20% off the Best Available Rate. Participating hotels in Asia Pacific offer up to 15% off the Best Available Rate. - Radisson Rewards members can receive up to an additional 10% discount when booking this rate direct. Members must be logged in during the booking process to see the additional discount. - The Prepaid Rate is a points eligible offer. Members will earn the standard 20 points per U.S. dollar spent, in addition to any applicable Elite tier status point bonus. - The Prepaid Rate and the Best Available Rate vary by hotel, are subject to change, and may be different each night of stay. - The offer depends on individual hotel's booking terms and conditions. - Offer is valid at participating hotels only and is subject to availability. The Prepaid Rate may be changed or discontinued at any time. Blackout dates may apply. - For the hotels in the Asia Pacific, the Prepaid Rate requires booking a minimum of 3 days in advance and varies by hotel. - The Prepaid Rate requires payment in full by credit card, e-wallet or Alipay for the entire stay at the time of booking. - The name on the reservation must be the same as the credit cardholder’s name, and the same individual must check in for the stay. - Reservations cannot be cancelled, amended or adjusted after booking. If you do not arrive on the reservation date, your reservation will be cancelled without refund or credit. - The Prepaid Rate is available for individual bookings only and cannot be combined with any other promotional or discounted offer. - Participating hotels are subject to change at any time without notice, and the number of rooms available for this offer may be limited and may vary by hotel. - Subject to applicable law and void where prohibited by law. - Additional taxes and surcharges may apply to the displayed rate. Total estimated rate is only available in the hotel's local currency. - Currency conversion is for comparison only. Currency rates utilized in each conversion example rely on several different public sources from other parties without independent investigation or verification and should be used only as examples. Radisson Hotel Group does not and cannot verify the accuracy of any of the rate of conversion examples, and actual rates may vary at any time and from time to time. - Radisson Hotel Group or its subsidiaries are the owners of the hotel brand names and Radisson Rewards.

column2: April Sales: up to 25% Discount on Radisson Hotels
column3: It's time to start looking forward to traveling again. Whenever you’re ready to start traveling, we’re ready to welcome you. column2: Art'otels | book in advance & save up to 20%

Stay at a participating hotel in Germany, Hungary or the Netherlands and benefit from a 10 - 20% discount off the Best Flexible Rate when you book a minimum of 7-30 days in advance.. - Subject to availability. - Valid at participating hotels only. - Advance booking period varies from 7 - 30 days in advance and qualifies for between 10 - 20% off Best Flexible Rate. - Advance Saver Rate is for room only and excludes breakfast. - Advance Saver Bed & Breakfast Rate includes breakfast and children 12 and under eat breakfast for free. - Minimum payment of 1 night only is pre-payable and non-refundable.
